    <item>
      <title>墨西哥重要财政官员将在过渡期间离职</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-27/key-mexican-finance-official-to-leave-in-presidential-transition</link>
      <description><![CDATA[当选总统克劳迪娅·谢因鲍姆 (Claudia Sheinbaum) 证实，墨西哥财政部级别第二高、任期最长的高级官员即将离职，这一消息在权力交接过程中令人意外，因为官员们一直向投资者强调权力交接的连续性。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-27/key-mexican-finance-official-to-leave-in-presidential-transition</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 27 Sep 2024 19:07:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>农作物贸易商 Olam 因延迟提交棉花销售报告被罚款 330 万美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-27/olam-to-pay-3-3-million-fine-for-delayed-cotton-sales-reports</link>
      <description><![CDATA[农作物贸易商奥兰集团有限公司 (Olam Group Ltd.) 因延迟向美国农业部和商品期货交易委员会报告棉花销售情况，将支付 330 万美元罚款，此举可能会影响棉花价格。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-27/olam-to-pay-3-3-million-fine-for-delayed-cotton-sales-reports</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 27 Sep 2024 18:48:14 GMT</pubDate>
